15:17.208 --> 15:20.961
Dude, you told me

15:17.208 --> 15:20.961
that was real.

15:21.003 --> 15:22.672
Now...

15:22.714 --> 15:25.633
let's talk business.

15:25.675 --> 15:27.134
(chortling)

15:27.176 --> 15:29.011
Craig, I can't

15:27.176 --> 15:29.011
