15:29.053 --> 15:30.179
That was fantastic!

15:30.221 --> 15:32.891
You were so heroic.

15:32.932 --> 15:34.601
I like to think we all have

15:34.642 --> 15:36.811
a little bit of Aquaman

15:34.642 --> 15:36.811
right here.

15:36.853 --> 15:38.979
Well, I must say, you

15:36.853 --> 15:38.979
really know your stuff.

15:39.021 --> 15:40.440
I'm impressed.

15:40.481 --> 15:42.776
Well, you know...

15:40.481 --> 15:42.776
if you're interested,

15:42.817 --> 15:44.985
there is a convention

15:42.817 --> 15:44.985
next Saturday.

15:45.027 --> 15:47.321
I have a life, Craig.

15:51.242 --> 15:52.744
(Malcolm grunting)

15:54.537 --> 15:57.206
MAN:

15:54.537 --> 15:57.206
Car number 15, no bumping.

15:57.248 --> 15:58.416
Return to the pit area.

15:58.458 --> 15:59.459
What the hell are you doing?!

15:59.500 --> 16:00.835
MALCOLM:

15:59.500 --> 16:00.835
You had no right!

16:00.877 --> 16:02.879
You stole from me!

16:00.877 --> 16:02.879
That was my money!

16:02.921 --> 16:04.380
Fine. Let's see.

16:04.422 --> 16:06.006
I've done 63 laps.

16:06.048 --> 16:07.300
Keep the change!

16:07.341 --> 16:09.009
MAN:

16:07.341 --> 16:09.009
Car eight, let's be courteous.

16:09.051 --> 16:10.678
It ends here, Reese!

16:10.720 --> 16:12.388
I don't care about the money!

16:12.430 --> 16:14.056
I don't care about my birthday!

16:14.098 --> 16:16.392
I don't care about your safety

16:14.098 --> 16:16.392
or mine!

16:16.434 --> 16:19.604
I don't care about anything

16:16.434 --> 16:19.604
except making you suffer!

16:19.646 --> 16:21.021
Well, I don't care either!

16:21.063 --> 16:24.442
Fine! Let's see

16:21.063 --> 16:24.442
