16:28.279 --> 16:30.865
This is a game of chicken

16:28.279 --> 16:30.865
Reese is not going to win!

16:30.907 --> 16:33.033
I'm too angry to blink!

16:30.907 --> 16:33.033
When he sees my face,

16:33.075 --> 16:34.911
he's going to know

16:33.075 --> 16:34.911
