17:11.113 --> 17:13.658
you're grounded, again.

17:13.700 --> 17:15.576
Thanks for getting me

17:13.700 --> 17:15.576
grounded on my birthday.

17:15.618 --> 17:17.495
Oh, boo-hoo,

17:15.618 --> 17:17.495
I was grounded on my birthday.

17:17.537 --> 17:19.873
MALCOLM: I was just

17:17.537 --> 17:19.873
standing up for myself.

17:19.914 --> 17:21.749
There is such a thing

17:19.914 --> 17:21.749
as justice, you know!

17:21.791 --> 17:23.125
Well, there is such a thing

17:21.791 --> 17:23.125
as "shut up!"

17:23.167 --> 17:25.085
Stop it.

17:25.127 --> 17:26.295
Malcolm, do you remember

17:26.337 --> 17:28.088
what you did for your birthday

17:26.337 --> 17:28.088
last year?

17:28.130 --> 17:30.090
Nothing. I was

17:28.130 --> 17:30.090
grounded then, too.

17:30.132 --> 17:31.091
And what about your birthday?

17:31.133 --> 17:32.092
You grounded me after

17:32.134 --> 17:34.012
I smashed Malcolm's face

17:32.134 --> 17:34.012
into the cake.

17:34.053 --> 17:35.429
And your birthday before that?

17:36.639 --> 17:37.807
Pretty much this.

17:37.849 --> 17:38.975
Wait.

17:39.017 --> 17:40.142
When did you push me

17:39.017 --> 17:40.142
off the pony?

17:40.184 --> 17:42.520
Do you realize

17:40.184 --> 17:42.520
that neither of you

17:42.562 --> 17:45.982
