18:02.081 --> 18:03.708
Is it worth it now?

18:03.750 --> 18:06.126
Do you feel happy?

18:06.168 --> 18:08.046
There's no reason to

18:06.168 --> 18:08.046
compete with each other.

18:08.087 --> 18:10.172
We love you

18:08.087 --> 18:10.172
both the same.

18:10.214 --> 18:13.133
There are no favorites

18:10.214 --> 18:13.133
in this family.

18:13.175 --> 18:15.094
Where  is  Dewey?

18:21.434 --> 18:24.103
I said, there's

18:21.434 --> 18:24.103
Mr. Lincoln now.

