19:53.442 --> 19:55.736
You know what will help us?

19:53.442 --> 19:55.736
The bullet.

19:55.778 --> 19:58.322
The bullet is always the answer.

19:58.364 --> 20:00.282
Oh, my God, it is here!

20:00.324 --> 20:01.492
That's it!

20:01.534 --> 20:03.202
I know what we have to do!

20:04.286 --> 20:08.499
Ah! Oh! Francis! Oof!

20:08.541 --> 20:09.667
